data.description: This beautifully maintained lakefront home comes fully furnished and with a boat slip in a community dock available to purchase. Open floor plan on both floors offer views to the lake. Five bedrooms for family and friends to visit. Large deck and porch for outdoor entertaining. Easy walk to the lake. Fireplace upstairs and down. This home is furnished and ready for your enjoyment!
data.whatILove: With all the windows on the back wall, the views are beautiful and there is so much light. I love watching nature in the backyard off the back deck.  The walk to the water makes it easy to fish off shore.
